Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy and Carla joined our guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and things have gotten lively again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts came back, too... I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing that I \Nwonder about, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Mystogan too, right? What is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:01:59.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither is this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander and that new brat both have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So why am I the only Dragon \NSlayer without a cat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have any figures of Gajeel left?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must be a real hard-core fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we have some, most definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even got a stand for \Nthe cat, just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Totally gnarly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we designed it with \Nthe future in mind, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! It's only noon, \Nwould you pipe down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk, when you're \Nalready drinking at noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, man... God knows what \Nyou're doing to your stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} not bothering anyone, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A book of poetry written in ancient Harukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient Harukan... Do you mean it's \Nwritten in some ancient language?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy, you're so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,July 7th, 777...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragons that taught Natsu-san \Nand me Dragon Slayer magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,both disappeared on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:05.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu might have mentioned that Gajeel's \Ndragon vanished the same day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they all went camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, you say some \Nstrange things sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All set...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Dragon Igneel, the Iron Dragon \NMetalicana, and the Sky Dragon Grandine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where they all are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:37.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish I caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I could \Ngive it to you, Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then, what do you \Nlike? Next time, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hanging around me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:07.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla! Don't you think that was mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, yeah, right... \NWhat's happy about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know a damn thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Carla is oddly cold to Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought I told you \Nto stop hanging around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I, maybe, do something wrong to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:14.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I \Nwill protect Wendy, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can protect Natsu, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu calls me his partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat who doesn't even know \Nwhat he is, like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the scratches?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut yer trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:24.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold without \Nan umbrella like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So will you, Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, it hasn't been that long \Nsince we joined this guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think you have to try and \Nget along more with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have to be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought \Nyou would come to this guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the meaning of this? \NI thought you were captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a different person than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're clearly Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mystogan, a member of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While I knew hardly anything about this \Nworld, I gave my name to you as Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:06.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one from seven years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Jellal from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I wasn't able to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Now is not the time \Nfor happy reunions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without delay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from this city, without delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have failed in my mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. It'll be \Ndangerous to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anima has grown too large for \Nmy power alone to suppress it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, Magnolia will be wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're saying at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over. The destruction \Nis already certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone in the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:02.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain just isn't stopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not think it is Juvia's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna sleep, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's scribble on his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What about everyone in the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that everyone will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:39.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to warn everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go! You, at least, \Nshould leave the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By myself? I could never think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a member of Fairy Tail now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, please stop these \Nkinds of childish pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you callin' a child, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're even worse than a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you muttering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:24.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man! You people need to be more \Nassertive! And you call yourself a Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who drew this on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one other person \Nwho'd stoop to your level, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go, bud?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I punished you for your \Nloud-ass snoring, is what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama... You look so \Ndreamy when you're fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainy days are perfect for going \Non dates with your boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, make sure to leave enough of your \N"boyfriend" to serve guests, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where are you going \Non a day like this, Mira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Man, then get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to protect Levy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell 'em too, Neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They totally screwed up on their last job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:27.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They got knocked out first, and Levy had \Nto finish up the job all by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts to hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We suck so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Jet and Droy were doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...such as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I could at least save Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are Mira-san and Elfman going \Nto the church on a day like today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost the anniversary \Nof Lisanna's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira and Elfman's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was two years ago... An accident on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:29.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets close to the anniversary, \Nthose two start start going to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:37.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, you \Nremind me a bit of Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how you get along well with Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... That guy's got too much energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Asleep already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Natsu used to have a girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you eat it without \Ngetting it everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time Juvia has eaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There they go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat a caramelized frank like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You open your mouth really wide and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't so high class food, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it's probably best not to strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they be so bold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Bisca and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain just isn't stopping, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you two are as friendly as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherish this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have any regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Erza! Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that 100-year quest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking into it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of giving it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there's nothing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With it raining like this, it's hard \Nto get motivated to go on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish something interesting would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anima is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we have trouble! The sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild has... vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the entire city, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the city and \Nguild are all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone left other than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A hole suddenly appeared in the sky \Nand sucked up the guild and the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:17.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling the truth! It looks \Nlike we're the only ones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:22.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, did you bump your head \Nor something? That's nuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's only Dragon Slayers that are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:41.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank the special magic \Npower you have as a Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:45.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that at least you two are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't gonna cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you don't give \Na crap about the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... They're really gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:54.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone. Or, more precisely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been sucked into Anima and wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anima?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole in the sky from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the gate to Edolas, the \Nworld on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What the hell have you been saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Carla... Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, why are you okay, Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from the other world, Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so has that he-cat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason this city disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is because of the he-cat and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, have you heard there's another \Nworld that resembles this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of those things, \Nyou know... A parasol world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:05.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you mean "parallel world".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it's a world that's kind of \Nlike ours, but with some differences...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about this something-or-other world?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:21.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, maybe in \Nthat world I'm a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:24.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a king, Happy, then I'd be a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
